Introduction

MUU is a South Korean singer. She is a former member of the girl groups LUNARSOLAR and A-Daily under the stage name Taeryeong, as well as a pre-debut member of BLACKMAMBA. She made her solo debut on September 17, 2022, with the digital single "Happy Trip" under the stage name Taeryeong.
